race.description: Tooheys How Do You Feel Maiden Handicap
race.comment: MATIAS (1) four-start Maiden ready to land his breakthrough victory. Slow into stride and attacked the line strongly when an unlucky second over 1550m at Canterbury. Should get the right tempo to finish over the top of these. WAR KING (5) comes out of a solid Super Maiden at his second run back when a fast finishing fourth over 1400m at Rosehill. Near his top now and will relish the Newcastle track. ENTRAPMENT (11) covered plenty of ground at her first run back when a gritty on-pace third over 1300m at Kembla Grange. Drawn out again and not without each way prospects. VELIA (6) resumed over the unsuitable trip when a respectable fourth over 1300m at Kembla Grange. This trip suits and shouldn't be a Maiden for long. WIZARD'S STAR (12) found the 1300m too short first-up, and wasn't that far away in town last prep. One for the exotics.
